{% doc %}
  @prompt
    make a best seller module  adding products from the catalog 
    
    - product photo (linked to the product page)
    - Title (linked to the product page)
    - Description 
    - Price ( add From before the price )
    - Color variants ( show if the product has  color variants)
    
    This module should be easy to adjust an has adjustment for each part of it. 
    
    it has a slider function that work in mobile and desktop, do not have navigation buttons,  people can slide with the mouse or the touch.   It has  a function that slide automatic  (10 to 20 seconds ) can be turned off.  
    
    
    Typography options like, weight, color, size, etc
    
     The maximum area for the content is 1500px, Use the default template  font.
    
    The content should fit into 1500px, limit the content to fit in 1500px, The border color, for card and effects can be adjustable., Description length can be adjusted to 1 or 2 lines, add after the product title a custom text  option
    
    add after the product description a custom text option, add  custom text  after title and custom text after description for each product, change the product decription to limit character from 50 to 200, replace the description for   product.metafields.custom.sub_title, subtitle character limit starting at 10
    
    space of content Limited  to 1500px
    
    Add Title withh the options ( by default. Best Sellers), title: use the default template font, aligment to the left 
    
    the frame  is maximum 1500px width
    
    add this snippet after the title for reviews make it easy to adjust: {% render 'junip-product-summary', product: product %}, The content should fit into 1500px, limit the content to fit in 1500px
    
    add option to adjust all the text weight, for all the variants add options to change the spacing from 0 to 10px
    
    add adjustments for the photo 
    
    the content should fit into 1500px width container, itÂ´s not full width, make the  width of the content including title and card adjustable from 800px to 1500 px, force the modulo to live inside 1500px, show 5 products cards by default 
    
    the the space between each card can be adjustable from 0px to 30px
    
    adjust the width and height of the photos

